## Default domain translations (English).
##
## String-based msgids — the English text is the key.
## Platform overrides go in platform-specific .po files (acme.po, peek.po, etc.).
## Non-English translations go in the locale's default.po (fr/default.po, etc.).
##
## English entries with msgstr "" are tracked by mix gettext.extract;
## gettext returns the msgid (English) when msgstr is empty.

